{"tid":1313924,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"停一停，諗一諗","createTime":"2019-07-14T03:22:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-14T04:13:22.000Z","uid":66830,"like":3,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"96d1460a9040a69b9e4e3e9c84a3320f79e3fba8","tid":1313924,"uid":66830,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T03:22:56.000Z","msg":"喺熱門見到有人想飲下雞尾酒，仲有三千幾正評，雖然係兄弟爬山，但係當啲狗受到「生命威脅」，加上而家瘋狗症肆虐，<span style=\"color: red;\">我怕最前線啲兄弟會食實蛋，造成大量兄弟傷亡。</span><br />\n<br />\n除咗兄弟傷亡之外，更加有可能令到中間派/淺黃動搖，民意亦會隨之急速消耗，我明白前線兄弟，甚至香港市民已經充滿憤怒，但係正因為咁，我哋更加要忍，<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">因為一個錯誤就可能令到成場運動玩完</span></span>，我估林奠都深明哩個原因，佢就係等緊我哋犯錯。<br />\n<br />\n我哋喺度接觸到嘅只有其中一部分香港人，主要係年青一輩，接受程度會高，<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">可能有啲事情喺度會有好多人支持，但係返到現實社會又未必係咁。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n記住我哋嘅目標，並唔係要整傷狗隻，而係五大訴求。"},{"pid":"5f353bd89be1efe0198d60138cda394b92a5d7a0","tid":1313924,"uid":66830,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T03:23:21.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"13301f7ac8cc3d1ae90a5d679275dc34d56edcf2","tid":1313924,"uid":66830,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T03:23:32.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"866d78d79525b77304131a0c5e22df85ec2e6d8f","tid":1313924,"uid":66830,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T03:24:13.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"3b6e0e53ac3ca6a9a22202005cb847211ef1a086","tid":1313924,"uid":66830,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T03:24:26.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"2ba6b41b20625e27af0dd2e4c416964670925048","tid":1313924,"uid":115205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T04:03:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8bcfc892fa2ad9bd6d2d87e16095aa295f838960","tid":1313924,"uid":211428,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T04:13:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}